    {
      "id": "36",
      "name": "Properties",
      "components": [
        {
          "component_id": "customize",
          "data": {
            "data": {
              "parsed_content": [
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:rgb(255, 255, 255)"
                      ],
                      "text": "Relationships",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "level": 3,
                  "type": "heading"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "amount": 0,
                      "display_style": "card",
                      "ep_id": 3798,
                      "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/04/26/169177528/fe011f0f93e3259d28b0272d0db961b7_4214171043320223201.png",
                      "menu_id": 22,
                      "name": "Inazuma",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "Beelzebul is the current Electro Archon of Inazuma.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "amount": 0,
                      "display_style": "card",
                      "ep_id": 7088,
                      "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/10/12/237301566/93cd2bc9b90c8b87b1f8cbdbe95b4b9d_1107416649457146883.png",
                      "menu_id": 20,
                      "name": "Война Архонтов",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "Baal and Beelzebul won the Archon War together. For all the Inazumans there was only one Archon, Baal.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "amount": 0,
                      "display_style": "card",
                      "ep_id": 7089,
                      "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/10/12/237301566/93cd2bc9b90c8b87b1f8cbdbe95b4b9d_1090730713764694732.png",
                      "menu_id": 20,
                      "name": "Катаклизм в Каэнри'ах",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "During the Cataclysm, Makoto didn't tell Ei and went to",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "amount": 0,
                      "display_style": "text",
                      "ep_id": 4811,
                      "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/06/11/237301566/93cd2bc9b90c8b87b1f8cbdbe95b4b9d_705904275694017757.png",
                      "menu_id": 22,
                      "name": "Каэнри'ах",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "alone. She wasn't a good warrior so she died.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "amount": 0,
                      "display_style": "card",
                      "ep_id": 7498,
                      "icon_url": "",
                      "menu_id": 10,
                      "name": "Кицунэ Сайгу",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    },
                    {
                      "amount": 0,
                      "display_style": "card",
                      "ep_id": 7499,
                      "icon_url": "",
                      "menu_id": 10,
                      "name": "Сасаюри",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    },
                    {
                      "amount": 0,
                      "display_style": "card",
                      "ep_id": 7500,
                      "icon_url": "",
                      "menu_id": 10,
                      "name": "Микоси Тиё",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "Ei's friends",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "amount": 0,
                      "display_style": "card",
                      "ep_id": 4907,
                      "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2025/02/08/237301566/08ad31cb2d00748c8a122eb1c2562ff8_607942454148584632.png",
                      "menu_id": 10,
                      "name": "Makoto",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "Makoto is Ei's twin sister. During Makoto's reign, she was her kagemusha. When Ei found her sister in Khaenri'ah, it was too late. They could say goodbye in Makoto's unconsciousness, but Ei didn't find out why her sister left alone.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "Plane of Euthymia",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "After Makoto's death, Ei placed her consciousness inside the Musou Isshin and created a sub-space, the Plane of Euthymia, where she meditated for centuries.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "amount": 0,
                      "display_style": "card",
                      "ep_id": 7,
                      "icon_url": "https://bbs.hoyolab.com/hoyowiki/picture/character/Yae Miko_icon.png",
                      "menu_id": 2,
                      "name": "Yae Miko",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "Ei's friend and familiar. Thanks to her help, Beelzebul left the Plane of Euthymia and cancelled the Vision Hunt Decree. When Ei went to the Plane of Euthymia, she left Miko her",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "amount": 0,
                      "display_style": "text",
                      "ep_id": 4935,
                      "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/02/15/94376896/d233949972be14fcf0feb738a9b67efa_4817492893140404510.png",
                      "menu_id": 20,
                      "name": "Gnosis",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": ".",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "amount": 0,
                      "display_style": "card",
                      "ep_id": 4583,
                      "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/11/09/151578876/3ca9b9e2138195540f079c470acfbce5_2205193756032034346.png",
                      "menu_id": 10,
                      "name": "Scaramouche",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "Raiden Ei created Scaramouche as a prototype puppet to prove the concept of creating a puppet body. At first, Ei wanted to get rid of him, but then he sealed his power and left it in the Shakkei Pavilion with a golden feather, signifying the relationship with the Shogun.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "amount": 0,
                      "display_style": "card",
                      "ep_id": 49,
                      "icon_url": "https://bbs.hoyolab.com/hoyowiki/picture/character/Raiden Shogun_icon.png",
                      "menu_id": 2,
                      "name": "Raiden Shogun",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    },
                    {
                      "amount": 0,
                      "display_style": "card",
                      "ep_id": 2210,
                      "icon_url": "https://bbs.hoyolab.com/hoyowiki/picture/enemy/Magatsu Mitake Narukami no Mikoto_icon.png",
                      "menu_id": 7,
                      "name": "Magatsu Mitake Narukami no Mikoto",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "A puppet, who has been ruling Inazuma after Ei went to the Plane of Euthymia. Currently, Ei shares the body with the Shogun.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "amount": 0,
                      "display_style": "card",
                      "ep_id": 4908,
                      "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/02/20/237301566/1397393f5024f3cfe3e0cd632dae57a6_3946025652687587216.png",
                      "menu_id": 10,
                      "name": "Оробаси",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "Around 2,000 years ago, Orobashi and Watatsumi's forces rebelled against the Narukami, and Raiden Ei destroyed him with the Musou no Hitotachi, cutting Yashiori Island in two.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "amount": 0,
                      "display_style": "card",
                      "ep_id": 4909,
                      "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/02/20/237301566/60104b9d7f3e714c49d7ac7f92758a63_6366136836730839877.png",
                      "menu_id": 10,
                      "name": "Канна Капацири",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "Beelzebul destroyed Kanna Kapatcir as a dangerous being that threatened the safety of Inazuma.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "amount": 0,
                      "display_style": "card",
                      "ep_id": 2454,
                      "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/09/26/124137736/5616b6b3139611441609112738d0b013_3450621923866854335.png",
                      "menu_id": 10,
                      "name": "Иорой",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "One day, Ei almost cut Ioroi in two when he was stealing Naku Weed in Tenshukaku.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
